hk:CityOfTears a hk:Regiao ; hk:nome "City of Tears" ; hk:fazFronteiraCom hk:RoyalWaterways, hk:KingdomsEdge, hk:RestingGrounds .
hk:RoyalWaterways a hk:Regiao ; hk:nome "Royal Waterways" ; hk:fazFronteiraCom hk:AncientBasin .
hk:AncientBasin a hk:Regiao ; hk:nome "Ancient Basin" ; hk:fazFronteiraCom hk:TheAbyss .
hk:TheAbyss a hk:Regiao ; hk:nome "The Abyss" .
hk:Deepnest a hk:Regiao ; hk:nome "Deepnest" ; hk:fazFronteiraCom hk:QueensGardens .
hk:QueensGardens a hk:Regiao ; hk:nome "Queen's Gardens" .
hk:CrystalPeak a hk:Regiao ; hk:nome "Crystal Peak" ; hk:fazFronteiraCom hk:RestingGrounds .
hk:RestingGrounds a hk:Regiao ; hk:nome "Resting Grounds" .
hk:KingdomsEdge a hk:Regiao ; hk:nome "Kingdom's Edge" ; hk:fazFronteiraCom hk:TheHive .
hk:TheHive a hk:Regiao ; hk:nome "The Hive" .
hk:HowlingCliffs a hk:Regiao ; hk:nome "Howling Cliffs" .
